I haven,t been here for some time. No one has for awhile I see. Glad to see its still here. <br>
  I didn,t think that I had a problem with the war anymore. The name of a friend that was killed in nam kept comming into my mind. We meet on our first day in contry. Went to the same recon unit in the 196th. I was with him when he died and then I stripped his body to send his body and possesions home. I couldn,t forget. <br>
  I talked to his mother the other day. I was finally able to tell her I was sorry. <br>
